    "body": "If you haven’t already, check out our [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/Expensify/ReactNativeChat/blob/main/contributingGuides/CONTRIBUTING.md) for onboarding and email contributors@expensify.com to request to join our Slack channel!\n___\n\n**Version Number:** 9.3.60-1\n**Reproducible in staging?:** Yes\n**Reproducible in production?:** Yes\n**If this was caught during regression testing, add the test name, ID and link from BrowserStack:** https://github.com/Expensify/App/pull/87577\n**Email or phone of affected tester (no customers):** ndk.2303+290@gmail.com\n**Issue reported by:** Applause Internal Team\n**Bug source:** Pull Request QA execution\n**Device used:** iPhone 11/iOS 26.3.1\n**App Component:** Left Hand Navigation (LHN)\n\n## Action Performed:\nPreconditions:\n- Log in as a workspace admin/auditor/approver whose workspace has expenses across 2+ months in the last 12 months\n\n1. Open Hybrid app\n2. Navigate to Home\n3. Navigate to Settings > Troubleshooting \n4. Clear cache and restart\n5. Go offline\n6. Navigtate to Home\n7. Scroll down to Spend Over Time chart\n\n## Expected Result:\nOffline indicator should be shown instead.\n\n## Actual Result:\nChart is displayed instead of Offline indicator\n\n## Workaround:\nUnknown\n\n## Platforms:\n- [ ] Android: App\n- [ ] Android: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] iOS: App\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Safari\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Chrome\n- [ ] Windows: Chrome\n- [ ] MacOS: Chrome / Safari\n\n## Screenshots/Videos\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/62122feb-7601-478d-b909-e4cc862e3a42\n\n[View all open jobs on GitHub](https://github.com/Expensify/App/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22Help+Wanted%22)\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @dmkt9</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022044800142818304078</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2044800142818304078</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-04-16</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
